In [32]:
for i in range(len(titles)):
    data = bank_dataset.pivot_table(index=titles[i], columns='Products', values='userid', aggfunc='count')
    data['sum'] = data.sum(axis=1)
    for j in range(1,5):
        data[j] = data[j] / data['sum']
    data.iloc[:,0:4].plot(kind='bar', figsize=(12, 7), grid=True, 
                          title='       ' + titles_russian[i])
    ax = plt.gca()
    plt.xticks(rotation=0);
